{"tid":2363960,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好怕凍，我開咗個純文字多女船P","createTime":"2021-01-12T14:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T15:48:28.000Z","uid":47374,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9788aa6d34d0bf7bf7652edd17c299dde32efd","tid":2363960,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"點呀，歡迎喎，飲杯嘢先，<br />\n西貢碼頭12點開船，遲到可能要遊水，<br />\n第一批水著俄羅斯Model 11點半到，<br />\n唔使扮晒嘢問佢地凍唔凍，<br />\n佢地會笑鳩你，好，希望各位盡興<br />\n<br />\n*免費，搞手唔求打和<br />\n*狗不得內進"},{"pid":"0754e1fd88eb8fea2d7aefaa40b93e698b61a8c8","tid":2363960,"uid":210363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"喂 女呢"},{"pid":"6e8ebbd7045da665f7f5f0a199b8d244ceefebd6","tid":2363960,"uid":47374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0754e1fd88eb8fea2d7aefaa40b93e698b61a8c8","tid":2363960,"uid":210363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"喂 女呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"11點半到"},{"pid":"9d2daf60f31afb7494de5b7979981276fa6b9490","tid":2363960,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"啲女走光"},{"pid":"89c7a91f6d5cf8b36b05131a64cb03273ed123bb","tid":2363960,"uid":329977,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期日，我唔去浦了。一早出海。 <br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻尼米茲級航空母艦，買的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zOVXNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zOVXNQ.jpg&h=684efcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxWTKsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxWTKsG.jpg&h=d72d138f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28vxfzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28vxfzm.jpg&h=3f701537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐五千人的，長一千幾呎。 <br />\n順便請咗私人教練，可以試揸F18戰機，觀賞西貢牛尾海一帶景色<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的二手運砂船，坐30人，工業風遊艇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZG8ymg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZG8ymg.jpg&h=0e82c46e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dV9hNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dV9hNX.jpg&h=d1b9a085&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFiyKsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFiyKsX.jpg&h=26957946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCNWHe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCNWHe5.jpg&h=f97ad295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒。 <br />\n<br />\n星期日 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，<strong><em>搞手只求平安回航</em></strong>，大家開開心心玩返日。"},{"pid":"fa5fd70d7f18c2f020219f08381fc65d8c82df16","tid":2363960,"uid":210363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8ebbd7045da665f7f5f0a199b8d244ceefebd6","tid":2363960,"uid":47374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0754e1fd88eb8fea2d7aefaa40b93e698b61a8c8","tid":2363960,"uid":210363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"喂 女呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"11點半到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"咁依家做咩 搞住基等？"},{"pid":"0ba049b80ffff9d8def99af833d7b52c145c0d25","tid":2363960,"uid":389214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"成班麻甩佬冇女喺度搞乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b35b43d6761da74cf82bcadba109007e6c2ffe","tid":2363960,"uid":47374,"like"